Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,1014 A.D. \NNORTHUMBRIA REGION, YORK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,DAY OF THE IMPERIAL COUNCIL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-There's so many soldiers here. \N-Of course there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Miscalculation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The elders are going to gather here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, the elders are going to eat all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, when he was about to get stabbed, \Nhe didn't even notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about what happened the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean the assassination attempt \Non the prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's awful to say this, \Nbut we can't ignore the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this means the king \Nhas chosen Harald, not Canute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely Canute's supporters are upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking too loudly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still just a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we must reconsider our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Thorkell has joined Canute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This more than compensates for the loss of Ragnar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorkell doesn't know how to govern.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too much for Canute to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, there's someone else who joined \NCanute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His name was Askeladd, "covered in ash."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've never heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lords!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,His Highness the king and His Highness the prince \Nare about to enter the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, lots of good food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Thorfinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to feel worried for your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No one here is so foolish \Nas to shed blood in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and walk! Don't drag your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a stupid kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you touch me \Nwith those dirty hands of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't ignore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay up, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way! Let us through!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be notified of your punishment later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What a time to cause trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he's the prince's guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The prince is attending \Nthe imperial council right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way his guard would be \Nwalking around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Elders of Denmark...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for gathering here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My long-awaited wish has finally come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This land, England, \Nhas finally come under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This achievement is all thanks to your \Nvaliant efforts in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, my old friend Thorkell...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and my son, Canute
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,have returned to us, \Nthanks to the protection of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an unexpected stroke of good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you've returned, Canute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put Mercia, part of our new territory, \Nunder your rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make this land a good country together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorkell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Support my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mercia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most prosperous land within England...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the rumors were just rumors after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You don't know that for sure. \NIf the rumors really are true,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,then of course he'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall reward you as well in accordance with \Nyour achievements in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us continue to fight with valor \Nin Ireland, our next battleground.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ireland is the land \Nwhere our previous king, King Harald,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,was humiliated by Brian Boru, that insolent tyrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The king is reacting just as I had expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This proves he has no counter to my strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a battle of wits, I'll come out ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Floki, I like that look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm going to have you \Ndraw a losing ticket this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's going to be in control of this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have all the pieces. I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,this land still harbors impudent fools \Nwho show no respect for their king.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to let you know about this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent a messenger to urge them \Nto become my vassals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,However, despite that, they refused twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If they are sowing seeds of rebellion \Nthat would threaten our new territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then we must do everything we can \Nto nip it in the bud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wales.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall show the inhabitants of Wales
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of the true king.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall attack in the coming spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it one of Canute's men?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Send him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not one of the prince's messengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a sailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from one of the traders
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that someone who looked like you was taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a panic, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's been 11 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How hard it must have been for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as that man is still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,your heart will never be at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say it's still not enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I still remember it as if it were only yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the crackling fire in the hearth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The delicious smell of the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Helga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ylva.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the smile on your face when you were a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was telling you the story \Nof how I got trapped in an ice floe
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,a long time ago in Brattalihd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I had run out of food \Nand my ship had been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My six friends had all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still kept walking across the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how stormy the sea is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how frozen the sea gets...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,a sailor is always fighting a battle against the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a warrior...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with their own honor at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When Thors died...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,when you disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I swore on my honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Thorfinn, I'm not saying this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying this for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bring you back to Iceland, your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my responsibility to Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, the lords of Schleswig.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Son of Eirik, Ivar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In appreciation of your achievements on the \Nbattlefield, the king is granting you silver and land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept his offering with gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But he looks normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now. It was only for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He turned pale when he heard Wales mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be something in Wales \Nthat turns out to be his weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm expressing my gratitude \Ntowards the god of harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you intend to get bigger \Nthan you already are? Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's going on, King Sweyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know about the connection \Nbetween me and Wales?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No. That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never told Floki about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he did know, he wouldn't mobilize \Nhis entire army just to piss me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it must be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The real problem is that Wales \Nis going to turn into a sea of fire in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Think. I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I solve this before spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I lead a revolt with the prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Thorkell's army of 500 men \Nare the only ones who I could count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Our army doesn't have enough men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take some time to convince \Nsome of the generals to join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I could instigate a rebellion among the English again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Wales would end up \Nbecoming the main battlefield anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to think of a plan that involves a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the king's assassins might try to go after \NCanute in the midst of the confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me about home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Far, far to the west, across the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,there lies a new world \Nwhere the trees are laden with fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and grassy plains cover the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Vinland.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Vinland!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After you go home and things have settled down, \Nlet's head for Vinland together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that Thors wanted to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thors came to Iceland to escape battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If he were still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he would have tried to go there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A place without slaves or war,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,where everyone can live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A warm and fertile land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's build a country like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's in Vinland...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's in Vinland, I'm sure we could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, speaking of Wales...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that's where you went when you were \Nrunning away from me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did the people of Wales help you Danes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother's grave is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That land...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The land is poor but the people are full of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the country my mother loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That information is just between us, tell no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His Highness Canute's vassal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd, son of Olaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is luck never on my side in the 11th hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:07.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,中身はなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:09.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へ…へぇ。ワインで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:15.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵隊がたくさんおるなァ\Nそりゃそうさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:18.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今日はこの家に族長が大勢集まるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:23.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はー…これみんな族長たちが食うんか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:53.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなことねぇよ。でな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:56.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アニキのやつ、刺されそうになったのに気付いてもいねぇんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:13.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴公。どう見るかね、先日の…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:16.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王子殿下の暗殺未遂…か
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:22.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,畏れ多いことであるが、噂もあながち見過ごせぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:27.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やはり陛下のお心はクヌート様よりハラルド様か。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クヌート派は面白くなかろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お声が高い。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ噂にすぎませんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:38.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,身の振り方を改めねばならんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:42.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやいや…クヌート派にはあのトルケル殿が加わった。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:46.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これはラグナルの損失を補って余りある
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:51.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルケル殿は政治のできぬ男だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:54.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クヌート様の器量では持て余すわい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:59.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そういえば…クヌート派にもう1人加わったのがいたな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:03.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,確かアシェラッド…“灰まみれ”とかいう…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さて。聞かぬ名だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:07.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,諸侯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご起立されよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:13.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王陛下と王子殿下のご入室である！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:41.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おォウ！ごちそうテンコ盛り！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィンはどうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さて。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:55.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まァ、御身の護衛に心配はありますまい。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:59.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さすがにこの場で刃傷沙汰に及ぶバカはおらんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:34.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,早く歩かんか！グズグズするな！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:45.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バカなガキだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉっ…！おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あァ？なんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:36.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだガキじゃねェかよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい待てコラ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:45.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きったねェ手で触りやがって！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何なんだこのガキはよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,無視してんじゃねェぞこの野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:54.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オイ！何とか言えよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:59.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オイオイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なめてんのかー？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:04.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,金払えオラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:18.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,テメッ！こンのや…ごぁッ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:31.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どけー！道をあけろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バカタレが！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,またお前かぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:47.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,正式な処罰は追って沙汰する！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:49.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ったくこの忙しい時に！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:54.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞くところでは殿下の護衛だとか…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:58.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下は今、御前会議に出席されておる！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:01.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,護衛が町なかをうろついてるわけなかろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:15.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,デンマークの族長諸賢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:19.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今日はよく集ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:24.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,積年の望みは叶い、
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:30.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ついにこの地イングランドは余の統べるところと相成った。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:35.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この良き日は、諸君らの奮戦あったればこそである
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:40.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,また…古き友トルケルと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が息子クヌートも、
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:48.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神々の加護により我がもとへと帰り来た。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,望外の喜びである
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よくぞ戻ったな。クヌート
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父はうれしいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:12.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたには新領より、マーシアの統治を任せる。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:17.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父と共に、この地をよき国にしようぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルケルよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:21.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,息子を助けてやってくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,余の願いじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:24.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,んっス
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,マーシア…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:29.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イングランドで最も豊かな土地を…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,噂はやはり噂にすぎませんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:36.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやわからぬぞ。真実であればこそ、
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:38.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ言うより他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:43.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,諸君らにも、戦果に相応した褒美を授ける。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:48.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,次なる戦地アイルランドにおいても存分に奮われよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:58.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,彼の地アイルランドはかつて不遜なる僭主ブライアン・ボルにより、
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:03.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,先王ハラルドが苦汁をなめさせられた因縁の地であり…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,勝てる！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:11.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王の反応はオレの予測の域を出ていねェ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:15.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレの作戦に対処しきれてねェ証拠だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,知恵比べなら主導権をとれる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フローキのだんないい顔だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:28.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたにゃ悪いが今後は損クジ引いてもらうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:33.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このケンカを仕切るのはオレだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:36.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,駒もそろってる。オレならやれる！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しかしだ諸君。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:49.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この地には未だ、王に対する畏れを知らぬ無礼な者どもがおる。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:52.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのことも話しておかねばならぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:59.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,余はきゃつらに、臣従を勧める使者を遣わした。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:05.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,にもかかわらず連中は、二度にわたってはねつけおった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:11.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこに新領を脅かす芽が育っておるなら、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まず全力をもって摘み取らねばならぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウェールズ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,彼の地の者どもに、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:29.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,真の王者の力がどれほどであるかを知らしめるのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来る春より進撃する。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,心得よ諸君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,起きろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:02.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞こえんのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お・き・ろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,面会だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クヌートの手下か…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:14.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,追い返せ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はァ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下のご使者のわけなかろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:20.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただの船乗りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:54.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前らしき男が連れていかれたと、
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:57.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,知り合いの商人に聞いてな…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,慌てたぞ。トルフィン…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,関係ねェ…だろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,11年…か…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どれほどつらい思いをしてきたか…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前の言うとおり…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ワシにはわからん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:33.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの男が生きている限り、
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,心が安らぐことはない。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:39.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ充分じゃないというなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きっと、そうなのだろう…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:58.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今でも昨日のように思い出すんじゃよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:03.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,パチパチとはぜる囲炉裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:06.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うまそうな鍋の匂い…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:07.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヘルガ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ユルヴァ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そして！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:18.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,幼いお前の笑顔をな…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:28.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,昔…ブラッタリーの沖で、
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,流氷に閉じ込められた話はしたな…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:42.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,食べ物はなくなり、船も潰れた。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:46.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,仲間6人はみんな死んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:58.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それでもワシはずっと…氷の上を歩き続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:02.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜだかわかるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:13.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どれほど荒んだ海であろうと、
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どれほど凍えた海だろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:42.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,船乗りは海と戦っとるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦士と同じように…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:50.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,己の誇りをかけてな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズが死んだ時…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前がいなくなった時…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:05.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ワシは、誇りにかけて誓った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:11.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからトルフィン！\Nこれは…お前のために言うんじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ワシのためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうあっても、お前を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:19.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,故郷のアイスランドへ連れて帰る。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:24.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが…トールズに対する、ワシのケジメだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,続いてシュレスヴィヒの諸侯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:38.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,エイリークの子、イーヴァル殿。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:39.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,御前に進まれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:46.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦功を評価し、陛下は貴殿に銀と領地を下賜される。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:48.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありがたく受け取られよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:56.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そしらぬふうに見えるがな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:59.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,先ほど一瞬のことです。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウェールズと聞いて顔色を変えました
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:09.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウェールズに、\Nあ奴めの弱みにつながる何かがあるやもしれませぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご留意下さいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなガツガツすんなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みっともねェ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:30.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うるへー！豊穣の神に感謝の気持ちを表明してんだィ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:34.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハッ…それ以上でかくなるつもりかよ。まったく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:36.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:42.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何なんだ！？どういうことだスヴェン王め！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:45.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレとウェールズのつながりを知ってる…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:48.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやそんなはずはねェ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フローキに話したことはねェ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:57.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,たとえ知っていたとしても、オレへの嫌がらせのためだけに\N全軍を動員するなんてことはありえねェ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:59.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なら…やっぱり偶然か…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや。そんなこたァどうでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:09.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,問題は…春にはウェールズが火の海になっちまうってことだ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クソッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,考えろ！時間はねェ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,春先までに何ができる！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:22.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王子を立てて反旗をひるがえす…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:26.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…まともに使えんのはトルケルの兵500だけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:29.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだまだ戦力差がありすぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:33.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,将軍たちを引き込むにも、根回しの時間が…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:37.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イングランドの連中をまたたきつけるってのはどうだ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:40.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメだ！結局はウェールズが主戦場になる！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦う方向で考えるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:48.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それに…ドサクサに乗じて、\N王の刺客がクヌート殿下を狙いに来るかもしれん…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:57.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,故郷…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今さら…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:17.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はるかな西、海の向こう…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,たわわに果実が実り、
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:28.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,真っ青な草原が波打つ新天地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヴィンランドだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:43.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヴィンランドだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:57.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,故郷に戻って、少し落ち着いたら…\N一緒に彼の地を目指そう！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:01.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんで…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前も言っていたじゃないか！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:08.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズも行きたがっていたと。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:15.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズは戦いを逃れてアイスランドに来たんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きていれば…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:27.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズも彼の地を目指したに違いない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:34.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴隷や戦もない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰もが平和に暮らせる、
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,豊かで暖かな地。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな国を作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヴィンランドなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:52.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヴィンランドなら、きっと…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:15.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そういや…ウェールズっていやァさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:21.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前、オレに追われてあそこに逃げ込んだじゃんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:27.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありゃ一体、どーゆーカラクリだったんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:33.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでウェールズ人たちが、デーン人のお前に味方したんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お袋の墓がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:45.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの地は…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレの故郷…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:53.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレの国だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:58.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,土地は貧しくとも、民は誇り高い。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:01.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お袋の愛した国だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:07.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そっかァ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:12.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そいつァま～…何だな。お気の毒様だな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:18.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この話は誰にも言うんじゃねェぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:20.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わあってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:24.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クヌート殿下の従士！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:27.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウォラフの子、アシェラッド殿。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:30.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,御前に進まれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:35.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,…ったく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:01.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレって奴ァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:08.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしてこう、土壇場のツキがないのかね…
